Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:01.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 虽然和学生会的人来过好几次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是一次都没有见过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是个连我们也感觉非常棘手的家里蹲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}家里蹲？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}恐怕是和魔女的能力有关
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小田切她们好像已经收集猿岛的情报了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.36,0:02:18.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}岂不是已经被抢先了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.86,0:02:19.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要怎么办的 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.03,0:02:21.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嘛 冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.78,0:02:22.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有招儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.66,0:02:26.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}强行突破
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.75,0:02:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷静 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.08,0:02:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Hi guys
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.37,0:02:30.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猿岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.96,0:02:33.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这个人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.34,0:02:35.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这人哪里像家里蹲啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:40.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对了 有件事想请你们帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.97,0:02:47.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说 为什么我们要来重新布置房间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.35,0:02:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}顺利的话 说不定能问出猿岛的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你也来搬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:02:59.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 这可是个好东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:02.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这面积真是美好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:03.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你TM快去干活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 猿岛 都弄完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你在睡觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:10.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.67,0:03:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}站住 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.83,0:03:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看看 你看看 这家伙哪里像是个家里蹲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.63,0:03:19.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哪像个因为啥烦恼而成为魔女的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.05,0:03:21.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然不知道是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:24.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但怎么想现在都是绝好的机会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.01,0:03:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}机会？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你快去亲她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那样有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.39,0:03:32.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也干不少活了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:35.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}倒不如就亲一下 即使这样她还欠你的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:38.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}必须的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.82,0:03:41.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话 就没有办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可别怪我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.12,0:03:53.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}救我 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宫村 你能先回去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.05,0:03:59.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚刚把你当力工使唤 抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没事 你刚刚说的救我 是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.72,0:04:10.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.52,0:04:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我早就知道你会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是听谁说的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是的 我能看见未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能看见…未来？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.37,0:04:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你脑子没什么问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不相信也可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过事实如此 你也不能不信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 应该说你只能相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最开始的时候只能预见短暂的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}比如 下节课是自习
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:50.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会有突击考试什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.43,0:04:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}突然有一天 我看见到了可怕的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}旧校舍发生火灾的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后我竟然成了纵火犯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相信我 不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.12,0:05:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我就决定不去学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这话对谁说都不会相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以就变成了家里蹲？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:22.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是啊 猿岛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你会说我只能相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:34.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你也在火灾现场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你和我都被当成了犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.86,0:05:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啥 为啥会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.69,0:05:43.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讨厌 我也想知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.57,0:05:46.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话虽如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过这样我就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.37,0:05:55.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不去学校 也是为了不和你产生交集
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:59.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}像这样和预见的未来一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.71,0:06:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和你相遇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个时候 我是该道歉么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不用 该道歉的应该是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说不定这样和你相遇 未来就会有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是未来不是这么容易就能改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.60,0:06:20.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说 猿岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:22.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我接个吻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.86,0:06:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就因为把你卷进来 所以要我用身体来偿还么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.61,0:06:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没说要到那个地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:30.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么做是另有深意的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.74,0:06:34.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总之 要找的真正的犯人 只能用这个方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:39.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是山田的话 没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.33,0:06:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.33,0:06:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最后的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.80,0:06:55.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没必要把舌头伸进来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:57.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:06:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无礼的家伙 好好听人说话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 猿岛玛利亚毫无疑问就是魔女了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:09.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然你们也无法掩饰惊讶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.36,0:07:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实关于她的能力 我已经大概清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.12,0:07:18.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过我没有告诉你们的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.87,0:07:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要我出手 这种事情就是轻松加愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么只打我？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.68,0:07:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哦 好厉害啊 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.89,0:07:42.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说会被小田切打 原来说的是这件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:45.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}预知未来的能力真的是好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.90,0:07:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就明确了猿岛是能预知未来的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:53.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接下来就是正题了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.45,0:07:56.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大家先看一下这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是爆炸啊 山田画匠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你该不会真的预见到了这个画面了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.12,0:08:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么可能 我看到的更加真实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是说旧校舍会发生火灾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和猿岛被当成犯人这件事才是重点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那的确是件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:16.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:18.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然已经预见到了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不快点找出真凶就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.06,0:08:21.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.35,0:08:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚才你和宫村接吻时看到的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.15,0:08:27.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能再告诉我一次吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:30.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石和伊藤俯视着我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.53,0:08:33.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的脸上清楚的印着掌印
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊 也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.99,0:08:39.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田你能看见自己的样子对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:41.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 那幅画也是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.41,0:08:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个果然是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.54,0:08:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们把它当成是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.33,0:08:48.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}然后当时宫村也在场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这么一说 宫村确实不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是这个样子的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.84,0:08:59.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和宫村接吻后预见的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看不到宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是代表什么意思呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许就是以宫村的视角看到的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.27,0:09:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}视角？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.02,0:09:07.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.23,0:09:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说 接吻之后能以对方的视角预见到自己的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:15.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你那个表情绝对是没有听明白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:19.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再好好看一遍这幅画
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.37,0:09:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在里面能看到山田和猿岛 也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.62,0:09:24.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:27.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 山田 你要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火灾现场还有另一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.25,0:09:32.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接过吻的对象中 你有没有头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:37.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有是有…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是有点不太好开口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.43,0:09:44.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我的男性朋友们…来着的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.73,0:09:45.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}男性朋友…们？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.44,0:09:49.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并不是恋爱关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}同是归国子女 碰巧关系比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.15,0:09:54.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为…为什么和我解释这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:57.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我那家伙的名字和住址
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:10:02.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 但是 他该不会就是纵火犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:04.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:07.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 和火灾有关系是肯定的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也…是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.58,0:10:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去找他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一步也不要离开家
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是山田你要小心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:21.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 因为山田和他见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}未来成了现实该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.31,0:10:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}椿剑太郎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}厉害 这都做得到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.40,0:10:36.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们可别小看真正的不良啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.99,0:10:38.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不良也无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在游戏里追求第一就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:42.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.74,0:10:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你是D班的椿剑太郎吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}下场定输赢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 你听见没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.96,0:10:54.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了 别碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.13,0:10:57.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别人说话你给我认真听 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:00.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么了 你这混蛋 不是b班的山田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}找我什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.89,0:11:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以说有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也有事要问你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.52,0:11:13.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你喜欢上白石了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是归国子女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.73,0:11:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以经常被别人捧着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石她对我不限一顾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}【这里是OP~MS】
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这实在太新鲜了 让我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.62,0:11:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之后 我就喜欢上白石了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:30.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真是个奇怪的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 我要向白石告白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.04,0:11:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天 在学校的中庭拜托帮我把白石叫出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:40.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等…明天什么的 也太突然了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:43.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这家伙是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.05,0:11:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然说实话我并不觉得白石会同意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.47,0:11:49.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}啊 真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好人啊 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 这家伙真的会在旧校舍放火吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.48,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就对这样的山田 透露下我的拿手绝活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个 在失落或者想要打起精神的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.24,0:12:07.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是一定会做的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.75,0:12:10.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.37,0:12:14.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里不是学校的旧校舍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:16.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火灾发生的现场啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.22,0:12:24.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}烹饪…教室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.56,0:12:37.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么想 就是这货没跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做好了 友情的见证
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.49,0:12:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这家伙引发的火灾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}诶 不吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.25,0:12:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火灾是今天？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:54.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要来学校？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:13:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊 老师说明天务必到校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.21,0:13:05.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田君 猿岛同学 还有椿同学
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:08.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这三人今天最终还是在学校聚齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:11.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不管怎么说都要阻止椿做天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.81,0:13:15.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}话说回来 失落的时候 吃天妇罗来打起精神是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:19.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想想昨天小田切给你的那巴掌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.65,0:13:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明明事先都知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么没有办法去改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.65,0:13:28.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你看到的未来 真的能被改变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.04,0:13:33.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这…这样只能去放手一搏了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:36.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算怎么做 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这不是山田吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:43.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是怎么一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:46.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时间都到了白石还没来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:48.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.14,0:13:49.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.68,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我连白都没告就被甩了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.18,0:13:58.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你会代替白石同学过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:13:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冷静一下 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.90,0:14:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你仔细听好我将要说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.61,0:14:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和我 接吻
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:12.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:15.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然我还是被甩了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想要用玩笑来安慰我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:19.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才不是玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是认真的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望你能回应山田的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这么说更容易弄混了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗 没想到会是山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}随你怎么想
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和这家伙交换 然后不去接近旧校舍的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}火灾应该就不会发生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.90,0:14:42.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只对白石有感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.32,0:14:43.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.19,0:14:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别介意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:46.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要说的好像我被甩了一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 这样一来只能硬来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上吧 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.45,0:14:50.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}趁现在 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.41,0:14:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:58.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这里面有很深奥的缘由
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这家伙挺强的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.01,0:15:09.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}做得到的话就来试试吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:13.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:15.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没想到椿那家伙竟然这么强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.60,0:15:17.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:19.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}果然是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.14,0:15:22.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就知道你们两个会一身狼狈的回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和伊藤同学接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:26.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}猿…猿岛？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:29.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小丽全部都告诉我了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.32,0:15:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前的事和魔女的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:35.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我还以为山田是自己一个人在努力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:37.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不…那个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}竟然还有这么好的同伴 为什么不告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你果然是乐天派啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是要怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没能和椿交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.26,0:15:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.55,0:15:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.43,0:15:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白…白石 只能让你接受他的告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.02,0:16:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 我有更好的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}椿君 等很久了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白…白石同学
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.73,0:16:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.07,0:16:10.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是刚到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我听山田同学说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.91,0:16:15.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你有话要对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.91,0:16:19.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同学 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:22.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从很久以前就对白石同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.16,0:16:23.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在那之前能听一下我的愿望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:28.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.55,0:16:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我希望你现在能跟我一起去买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.13,0:16:35.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}小雅的影像中出现了时钟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.55,0:16:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这就是火灾发生的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 在时间到来之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.89,0:16:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田把椿带出去就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.31,0:16:45.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}椿 怎…怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.02,0:16:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么赶快出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样应该就能改变未来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.12,0:17:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就不能好好聊天了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:02.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.87,0:17:06.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 就算是椿 在这种地方也不可能告白的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:11.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能行 只要再在这里逛一个小时…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.80,phone,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,320)\frz2.122}{\alpha&H04&}猿岛玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.80,0:17:12.80,phone,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,320)\frz2.122}{\blur11}猿岛玛利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是的 又有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.59,0:17:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别说改变未来了 情况更加恶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.30,0:17:18.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:22.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来在活动室的小雅来到了火灾现场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:25.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到底在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.27,0:17:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}抱歉 我等下再打给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.36,0:17:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.19,0:17:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事情我已经听说了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.32,0:17:34.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 宫村 现在该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.86,0:17:35.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.70,0:17:39.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}起码知道了 未来确实在改变
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:43.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能是你们的身体互换改变了未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.87,0:17:45.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:48.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到这地步了没办法 用最后那招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.54,0:17:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然不得不回应告白 索性就让他延期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:55.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.38,0:17:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对不起 刚刚开始一直电话不停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.68,0:18:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有点急事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.97,0:18:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我还什么都没说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:07.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天 再说吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托 要答应啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了 明天也能见到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好 没有情绪低落
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 那我先赶时间
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.36,0:18:20.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 白石同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.50,0:18:27.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么样 宫村
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.16,0:18:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是白痴吗 赶快离开那里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.30,0:18:38.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么回事 这个浪漫气氛爆棚的地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.63,0:18:40.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同学
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.47,0:18:43.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等不到明天了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.98,0:18:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么 怎么会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请和我交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.12,0:19:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}该怎么回应…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这样的话…对不起了白石…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:10.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}嗯 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以等一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.63,0:19:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喂 白…不山田…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.46,0:19:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:31.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.94,0:19:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们两个 就是这种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.53,0:19:44.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}等等 椿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.28,0:19:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石你这家伙 想做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有这个办法
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.54,0:19:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}搞不懂你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.75,0:19:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:54.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}和他交换身体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.34,0:20:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好了 快开门椿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:04.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}闭嘴山田 我再不相信任何人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.35,0:20:08.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}先是被诱惑我的白石甩了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.10,0:20:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又被身为好朋友的你背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:12.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都说了那是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.98,0:20:13.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}居然锁上了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}拜托了 只有天妇罗千万不要碰
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田君 快离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.40,0:20:23.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.20,0:20:27.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}已经过了火灾的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.26,0:20:46.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}成 成功了我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:50.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们 拯救了大家的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.49,0:21:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和山田交换身体 原来是因为魔女的力量吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:07.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:08.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.53,0:21:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那让我也加入超研部吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:14.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.96,0:21:17.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}经过这次我也对魔女的力量感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是为了泡小丽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.63,0:21:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎 怎么会 才不是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.80,0:21:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且 绝对不允许你在这里炸天妇罗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.13,0:21:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}不是说了我是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:28.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}说不定就是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.26,0:21:30.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}怎么能这么霸道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:30.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}出来一下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.22,0:21:34.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Thank you 山田
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.98,0:21:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不 不用在意 我也不想成为犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:41.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还害羞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.77,0:21:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是 有件事我比较在意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.94,0:21:44.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.03,0:21:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石那家伙 为什么要这么突然交换回来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没听她说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:56.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.79,0:22:01.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知道未来是那样 还能义无反顾的交换
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是吗 猿岛同学告诉你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:08.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.84,0:22:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}白石她 不希望你成为犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:15.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么 都过去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.49,0:22:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你以为我会这样说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.37,0:22:31.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别再做这种蠢事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.55,0:22:50.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.10,0:22:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么这么高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.60,0:23:00.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}真是领教到你的缠人了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an8\fs30}疼…疼…疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.85,0:23:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也是超研部的成员了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.57,0:23:06.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}哎呀 大家都在啊
